result.adr_address: 209 - 219 Wan Chai Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 209 - 219 Wan Chai Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.name: The Charterhouse Causeway Bay Hotel

reviews.text: Good location. Decent (if small) rooms. Attentive staff. Good for the budget. My regular budget hotel in HK.
Good price in a very good location. Staff were friendly and helpful. Room was clean and comfortable.

I found this hotel most accommodating, set in a perfect location handy for walking around town or catching the local transport. A great selection of breakfast dishes, good choice of dinner dishes  and reasonable prices for the rooms, would definitely come again.

Slightly more modern style for a business hotel (loan phone, apps preloaded to support you when your arrive in Hong Kong, active engagement from the staff) at a very decent price. Has a couple of nice bars and restaurants around, and while the rooms and hotel itself doesn't offer many frills, it's neat, clean and had what you need for a quick business visit in Hong Kong on a budget.
Near to d bus station, market, masjid, halal food, teng teng odong odong or double decker

result.adr_address: 香港灣仔灣仔道209 - 219號
result.name: 香港銅鑼灣利景酒店

reviews.text: 一間性價比極高的標準四星酒店👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼

一開始是因為飯店有附handy phone 又比週邊的大品牌連鎖飯店低價才預定，入住後發現住房空間略微狹小(雖然知道陳舊但是意料之外的老舊)，沒地方放置行李、一開始浴室霉味開冷氣後有改善、浴室的沐浴乳是塑膠軟盒在長久使用下來有漏氣使得沐浴乳下不來；後來午睡時冷氣大漏水(與櫃檯反應之後有維護處理)，後來回房看還不錯；因為一家三口出行能省就省囉。
樓下周圍生活機能強大，多間茶餐廳與咖啡廳可供選擇。步行幾條街(約莫五分鐘)外就是知名百貨公司。
食物有水準，價錢合理，但款式比較少
